Compatible with iOS 10.1.1 and till 12.4 (Including arm64e/A12 Devices).

TunnelFolders is a Tiny Tweak that Allows to Get Tunnel Effect View when opening the Folders of Your SpringBoard!

On iOS 10 the Effects are Also when opening Apps!

The Tweak is now out from the Beta Stage of My Repository also Bringing arm64e/A12 Devices Support.
If you Have got My Repo Version, Just Uninstall it and Install this New One.

No options to Configure.

See Video below.
